                "text": "AI agent autonomy and misuse threats"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Threats arising from autonomous agent behavior, including uncontrolled tool use, excessive autonomy, agent-to-agent trust violations, lack of human oversight in high-impact operations, and human-trust-exploitation patterns on consumer-facing AI surfaces (OWASP ASI09:2026)."
              },
