            "control-effectiveness": "none",
            "inherent-risk": "7.8",
            "residual-risk": "7.8",
            "maestro-layer": "Unclassified",
            "recommendation": "Implement multi-factor authentication and session-token binding at the User-Zone-to-Application-Zone boundary. Deploy short-lived JWTs with rotation, session binding to device fingerprint, and server-side token revocation. Bind persona-state restoration strictly to the authenticated session identifier.",
            "effort-estimate": "High"
          }
        },
